title: Mediterranean Protein Roast — Balanced-Carb Edition 1
hydrationTip: Add 300–500 ml water with this balanced-carb lunch.
method: Heat olive oil in a pan.
Add chicken and cook until golden.
Add vegetables and cook until softened.
Stir in cooked rice and seasoning.
Portion evenly into four containers.
swaps: Swap chicken for turkey or tofu.
